<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - Goldmarks Jewellery</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1 style="color: #d4af37; margin: 0;">Goldmarks Jewellery</h1>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Password Reset Request</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
        <h3 style="color: #856404; margin: 0;">Password Reset Required</h3>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #d4af37; margin-top: 0;">{{subject}}</h2>
        {{{content}}}
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #f8d7da; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #721c24;">Security Notice</h4>
        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #721c24;">
            <li>This link expires in 1 hour</li>
            <li>Only use this link if you requested the reset</li>
            <li>Never share this email with others</li>
            <li>Contact us immediately if you didn't request this</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <footer style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;">
        <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Goldmarks Jewellery Team</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="#" style="color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">Contact Support</a> |
            <a href="#" style="color: #d4af37; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">Security Center</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>